  "title": "Viewer Role Capabilities",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "Viewers can search, list, and get nodes, track traversals, rate nodes (votes_up / votes_down), and use conversational Q&A. They cannot create, modify, or delete any nodes, edges, or workspace settings, nor can they propose changes."
